headline.print_headline: Potter, Shirley Lead in Women's Mid-Am Semifinals
headline.main: Potter, Shirley Lead in Women's Mid-Am Semifinals

lead_paragraph: Defending champion Julia Potter and 2013 runner-up Margaret Shirley led their semifinal matches Wednesday in the U.S. Women's Mid-Amateur when play was suspended because of rain.
